# DealRoom v3 — Testing (Updated)

> **Document status:** Reflects current passing tests plus new tests required
> for the four fixes. All currently-passing tests are documented as-is.
> New test sections are clearly marked.

---

## Test Suite Overview

Two execution contexts:

**HTTP tests** — run against live server at `http://127.0.0.1:7860`:
`test_00` through `test_05`, `test_09`, `test_11`

**Container unit tests** — run inside container via `docker exec`:
`test_06`, `test_07`, `test_08`, `test_10`, `test_scorer_unit`

The v3 suite (`tests/v3/`) is the primary validation suite.
Older directories (`tests/unit/`, `tests/integration/`) may contain legacy tests.

